title: Food Rules Part 2

description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Part 2 of the food rules we try to bring into every diet we begin. In this episode I talk honestly about an old keto diet I did that left me feeling terrible. You'll also learn: How do I find a diet that feels good? Are low carb diets what I need? Do I need protein shakes? Should I give up sugar? What do you think about elimination diets?
